&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the campaign concepting process end-to-end&lt;/strong&gt;, from identifying the insight (why this message, for this person, at this moment?) to translating it into a coherent campaign across email, direct mail, SMS, and the landing page.&lt;/li&gt;
